            <h2>An easy way to book your tickets</h2>
            <p>Spirit Airlines booking is a quick and easy process. You can find great <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/deals.aspx">deals on flights</a> and save money on extras such as baggage and priority boarding. With Spirit Airlines, you can find an affordable and convenient flight. </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Visit the Spirit Airlines website, www.spirit.com, and select the “Book a Flight” option. You will then be taken to a page where you can enter your travel details, such as departure and arrival cities, dates, and the number of passengers. After entering the information, you will be given a list of available flights. </li>
                <li>You can then select the Spirit flights that best suit your needs. Once you have chosen the flight, you will be taken to the page where you can enter your personal information and payment details. </li>
                <li>Once you have paid, you will receive an email with your confirmation number and other details. </li>
                <li>Finally, you can check in online before your flight by visiting the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/low-fare-calendar-spirit-airlines.aspx">Spirit Airlines flights</a> website. You must enter your confirmation number and other details to check-in. </li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Convenient baggage policies</h3>

            <p>Spirit Airlines cheap flights allow passengers to bring one personal item and carry-on bag onto the plane at no charge. Personal items must fit underneath the seat in front of you and may not exceed 18x14x8 inches (including handles and wheels). Carry-on bags may not exceed 22x18x10 inches (including handles and wheels). Passengers are allowed to bring a maximum of two checked bags per person. </p>

            <p>The first checked bag is subject to a fee of $30 each way, while additional bags are subject to a fee of $40 each way. Checked bags may not exceed 62 linear inches (length + width + height) and must not weigh more than 40 pounds. Spirit airlines always encourage customers to pack their luggage properly to minimize the number of bags used and eventually reduce the cost of carrying that baggage. </p>


            <h3>Reserve your seats without hassle</h3>

            <p><a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/spirit-airlines-flights-reservations.aspx">Spirit Airlines reservations</a> ensure customers receive fair and equitable service access. Customers must book their flights at least 24 hours before departure and no more than 11 months in advance. Customers can book flights online or through the Spirit Airlines call center. </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Spirit Airlines offers a variety of payment options, including credit cards, debit cards, and PayPal. Customers can also pay for reservations using their Spirit Airlines MasterCard or Spirit Airlines Visa. </li>
                <li>Spirit Airlines requires all passengers to provide valid identification during check-in. Customers must also present their confirmation number, provided when booking. </li>
                <li>Spirit Airlines allows customers to cancel their reservations 24 hours before departure without fees. Customers who must cancel within 24 hours of departure are subject to a cancellation fee. </li>
            </ul>


            <h3>Good news for Pet Owners</h3>

            <p>The Spirit Airlines Pet Policy allows passengers to travel with small domestic cats and dogs in the aircraft's cabin. To do so, passengers must <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">book a flight</a> at least 48 hours in advance and pay a fee of $110. The pet must be placed in a carrier no larger than 8.5" x 18" x 13.5" and fit comfortably under the seat in front of the passenger. Only one pet is allowed per passenger, and the number of animals allowed on a single flight is limited. </p>

            <p>Spirit Airlines also has a service animal policy, which allows service animals to travel in the cabin with their owners for no additional fee. To do so, passengers must provide documentation from their doctor or other medical professional verifying the need for the animal. Pet owners no longer have to leave their pets at home or under the care of strangers; they can easily carry their pets on their flights and go wherever they want. They only need to keep in mind the policies laid down by Spirit. </p>


